Browser DOM Context
===============================================================================

```mech:disabled
+> @ui := browser/dom

name := @ui/body/content/mech-sandbox/input/_value
@ui/body/content/mech-sandbox/output/_value = name
```

Configured DOM paths map to element text, attributes, or properties. Property paths such as `_value` expose DOM property values. Reads and writes require matching configured permissions. Denied writes are rejected before the host mutates the DOM.
